  "text": "Major considerations for developing landscape projection models should include an understanding of the main factors related to forest management (i.e., human-induced factors) which may affect forest landscapes in terms of composition and configuration [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Understanding these factors is a prerequisite to devise a more realistic and relevant foundation for developing landscape projection models that include forest management practices and their large-scale effects [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
